

Keywords:
		Search keywords: vmm_object create_by vmm_1.2

Technical content:
 
		Title: 		 vmm_object replacement 
 
		Objective:    replacing the vmm_object using create_by_new and copy

		Description:   This test shows the usageof  replacing the vmm_object blueprint class   using create_by_copy and create_by_new

		Additional setup: None	
 
 To run the example:
      Using Makefile:
       	clean           -- To clean up the log files and executable of previous run
       	comp            -- To compile the design
        run             -- To run the design
        all             -- It does all the above steps.
     Using shell scripts:
        clean.csh       -- To clean up the log files and executable of previous run
        comp.csh        -- To compile the design
        run.csh         -- To run the design  
 
 
Location Information:
		PATH: 			$VMM_HOME/examples/testbench/sv/vmm/std_lib/factory_pattern/basic_vmm_object
		DIAGRAMS: 		None
		Cross Reference:	$VMM_HOME/doc/vmm_user_guide.pdf
